<seg id="4"> Author: Just Sword </seg>
<seg id="5"> I remember that in the beginning of 2005, Apple Journal in Hong Kong published an article titled "Dharma Wheel Spins Constantly and Its Merits Can Overcome an Enemy Country." </seg>
<seg id="6"> The article alleged that 2004 was a year in which Falun Gong advanced rapidly while singing triumphant songs. </seg>
<seg id="7"> The article stated that overseas officials of the Chinese Communist Party acted like buffoons suppressing Falun Gong in various places, and totally lost face when beginning Falun Gong learners told the truths everywhere in the world. </seg>
<seg id="8"> But compared with the marvelous scene showing the great wave of Party membership withdrawal brought by the "Nine Comments" in 2005, 2004 does not seem outstanding. </seg>
