<seg id="11"> One is the article "Elimination of Evil" published by the founder of Falun Gong. This article announced and sentenced that those agents of the Chinese Communist Party will face their coming judgment day after July 20, 1999. </seg>
<seg id="12"> Maybe many people still have doubts about or disbelieve this article. </seg>
<seg id="13"> But no matter whether they believe it or not, the history and facts will prove it! </seg>
