<seg id="16"> But broad deaths or remorse of CCP agents at home and abroad brought by the Heavens will definitely bring powerful strikes and shake the power strata of the CCP. </seg>
<seg id="17"> They will have to carefully consider their path of retreat and road for life - withdrawal from the Party, desertion or changing their side under the awesome deterrence of the elimination brought by the Heavens. </seg>
<seg id="18"> Thus, the "superbly stable bureaucratic system and group of the CCP" will begin to be shaken, disrupted, and collapse! </seg>
<seg id="19"> The other event is the hunger strike campaign for human rights launched by Gao Zhicheng. </seg>
<seg id="20"> This suddenly arisen campaign, which did not receive a good prediction from some people in the beginning, unexpectedly brought warm reactions from everywhere in the world, and common responses from all strata and various forces. </seg>
<seg id="21"> If this activity can integrate various just forces and suffering masses into a connection and make it real and big, then the outside force that launches the final strike on the CCP, the evil regime that is as fragile as a pile of eggs, will finally be formed from it. </seg>
<seg id="22"> If we say that 2005 was a year when the Communist Party was eliminated from the perspective of the spiritual aspect, then 2006 will be the phase in which the Party will be gotten rid of in both the spiritual and material aspects. </seg>
<seg id="23"> With the further spread of the "Nine Comments" and further development of the wave of Party membership withdrawal, the self-disruption of the CCP, and the cohesion and formation of outside just forces, the life of the CCP monster will formally enter into a countdown state. </seg>
<seg id="24"> The wills of the Heavens and humans have been integrated, and the sacred power and human strength are gathering. </seg>
<seg id="25"> The long sword in the sky is directly pointed at the CCP monster! </seg>
<seg id="26"> If we say that 2004 was a year for advancing rapidly while singing triumphant songs, and 2005 is a marvelous year, then what will be the conclusion of 2006? </seg>
<seg id="27"> I hope it will be a shocking great change, and a victory and triumphant return! </seg>
