<seg id="13"> 4. Magician gives changes: Not all shop owners will swap your big bill, as that is against the law, and the risk is higher!</seg>
<seg id="14"> Therefore a few "timid" shop owners have to resort to being magicians. You clearly see him calculating the change to be correct, but wait till you have the chance to calculate on your own.  Ha-ha, it's short of a few bills.</seg>
